snippet.title: Women Power | South Superhit Movies | Jyothika, Nayanthara, Keerthy Suresh, Samantha
snippet.description:
Movie:- Madam Geeta Rani (Raatchasi)
Starcast:- Jyothika, Hareesh Peradi, Poornima Bhagyaraj, Sathyan, Nagineedu, Aruldoss

The film is about a headmaster converting a poorly run school into one of the best in the state.

Movie:- Tejasvini (Aramm)
Starcast:- Nayanthara, Sunu Lakshmi, Ramachandran Durairaj, Kitty, Vela Ramamoorthy

A little girl falls into a deep borewell, and her rescue becomes a huge professional and personal challenge for a collector.

Movie:- Mahanati
Starcast:- Keerthy Suresh, Dulquer Salmaan, Samantha, Vijay Deverakonda, Naga Chaitanya, Rajendra Prasad, Bhanupriya, Malavika Nair 

Savitri, the most admired actress from South Indian cinema, goes through various tragic incidents in her personal life. Unable to cope with depression, she eventually becomes an alcoholic.

Movie:- U Turn
Starcast:- Samantha Akkineni, Aadhi Pinisetty, Rahul Ravindran, Bhumika Chawla, Ravi Prakash, Ashish Vidyarthi

The plot revolves around the death of motorists who break a traffic rule at a particular flyover in Hyderabad and the subsequent pinning down of the culprit by an intern journalist and police inspector duo.

On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasimâ€™s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

snippet.title: Recipe 672: Thai Amavasai 2023
snippet.description:
The New Moon Day is called Amavasya or Amavasai. The Sanskrit word â€˜Amaâ€™ means â€˜togetherâ€™ and â€˜Vasyaâ€™ is â€˜to dwellâ€™. There is a cycle of 30 lunar phases as per the Vedic calendar and each of them is called a Thithi. The Thithi of the dark Moon, when the Moon is not seen in the sky, is referred to as Amavasya Thithi or simply as, Amavasya. 
Thai is the 10th month of the Tamil Calendar, which corresponds to mid-Januaryâ€“mid-February and is regarded as a very auspicious one. I
In 2023, Thai Amavasai for the month of January is on 21st. 

Following are the recipes and ingredients for the same : 

#Ingredients

#GodhumaiRava_Kesari

Ghee - 2 tbsp
Casew Nuts
Dry Grapes
Wheat Rava - 1 cup
Water - 3 cup
Country Sugar - 1 & 1/2 cup
Edible Camphor

#Sweet_Pachadi

Banana, Pomegranate, Apple
Grapes, Pineapple
Country Sugar - 1 cup
Water - 1/4 cup
Cardamom Powder - 1/4 spoon
Ghee small pinch
Roasted Nuts

#Vazhakkai_DeepRoast

Raw Banana - 2 (Diced)
Tamarind Water
Salt to taste
Turmeric Powder - 1/4 tsp
Oil - 4 spoon
Mustard - 1/4 spoon
Urad Dal - 1 spoon
Curry Leaves
Asafoetida Powder - 1/2 tsp
Homemade Sambar Powder - 1 & 1/2 spoon

#Vellarikkai_Kootu

Moong Dal (Boiled)
Cucumber - 1/2kg (Diced)
Salt - 1/2 tsp
Turmeric Powder - 3/4 tsp
Asafoetida Powder - 1/2 tsp
Grated Coconut - 4 spoon
Curry Leaves
Coconut Oil - 1 tsp
Mustard - 1/4 spoon
Urad Dal - 1/2 spoon
Dry Chilli - 1no

#Ellu_Sadham

White / Black Sesame - 4 spoon
Dry Chilli - 4 nos
UradDal - 3 spoon
Sesame Oil - 1 tbsp
Curry Leaves
Salt to taste

#PagarkaiThengai_Varutharicha_Kuzhambu

Toor Dal - 2 spoon
Gram Dal - 1 spoon
Fenugreek - 1/4 spoon
Dry Chilli - 4 to 5 nos
Oil - 2 drops
Curry Leaves
Grated Coconut - 4 spoon
Coconut Oil - 1 tbsp
Mustard - 1 tsp
Asafoetida
Dry Chilli - 2 nos
Bitter Gourd - 2 (Sliced)
Turmeric Powder - 1/4 spoon
Water as required
Salt to taste
Jaggery Small Piece

snippet.title: CARROT with EGG | Unique Carrot and Egg Recipe Cooking in Village | Chicken Inside Scrambled Omelet
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook the scrambled omelette recipe with using eggs and carrots. Usually, the Omelette recipe is one of the breakfast recipe, but we made it for full meals heaven. 

We add more flavor to omelette by using full chickens. We finally taste the scrambled omelette with chicken and mutton curry. The taste is the fullest!

Tere Bin Episode 09 Teaser - 19th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerabâ€™s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her familyâ€™s decision regarding her and Murtasimâ€™s life. Meerabâ€™s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerabâ€™s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasimâ€™s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3672 - 19 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3672: Bawri's Surprise
--------------------------------------------------------
About some alleged ghosts in their neighboring community, Madhvi tells Bhide. Bhide makes a call to the secretary of the neighboring society to find out the facts. He learns that some superstitious folks have been spreading the rumor of a ghost because of the flickering lights. Madhvi is instructed to reject such rubbish by Bhide. Later on that day, Bhide makes the decision to revise the ideas posted on the board of their Gokuldham society. Champaklal discovers Bhide's writing and confronts him about the shift, but Champaklal becomes terrified of the fictitious ghost. Will Bhide's ideas alter how people view superstitions? Remain tuned!

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Highlights! Man City 4-2 Tottenham Hotspur | Goals from Alvarez, Haaland and a Mahrez double
snippet.description:
City recovered from conceding two goals in two minutes at the end of the first-half to produce a stunning second 45 and beat Tottenham 4-2 on another memorable night at the Etihad Stadium.

The Blues were at their irresistible best when it was needed most to repeat Tottenham's feat by scoring twice in two minutes early after the break through Julian Alvarez and Erling Haaland.

Two more from the excellent Riyad Mahrez completed a superb comeback by City who had to dig deep to turn this game around.

snippet.title: Bakra Nahi Majnu Halaal - Part 2 : Full On Farziwada - Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Download Skkily Ludo App From 
https://bit.ly/Amit-bhadana

REFERRAL CODE - AMIT100


Jab aag lagi hai to dhamaka to ho kar rahega. Hamare Majnu ne le lie hain bade wala panga. 2 ladkiyon ko date toh bahut log karte hain lekin hamara hero 2 sagi behnon se pyar kar baitha hani. Lalach buri bala hain Rinku na Raveena se breakup karna chahata hai aur na hi Sangeeta ko ta-ta bye-bye, aur ab vo galti se pahunch gaya hain dono ke ghar jahan bas phootne hi wala hai uska bhaanda. Kya hoga aage isi baat ka hai sabko intezaar. Kya Sangeeta aur Raveena mil kar karengi Rinku ko halal ya unke papa karenge hamare Majnu ka kaam tamaam? Kya hoga is love story ka end? Ye sab pata chalega is part mein. To sab mil kar hamare Majnu ke lie prarthna karo aur poore parivaar family ke sath dekho ye kamaal dhamaal story. Dhnyaawad :)

snippet.description:
Episode 3671: Jetha Ki Anghooti
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha performs a prank on Bhide by asking him to search for his gold ring that has fallen from his balcony. He himself goes inside his house as Bhide searches for the gold ring. When Bhide gets to know about the prank, Jetha and Bhide get into a brief amusing quarrel. When Bhide calls Bapuji to take revenge, Bapuji chastises Jetha in retaliation. Jetha explains the true cause of Bhide's call, and Bapuji reprimands both of them. Tapu Sena arrives at Bhide's home and partakes in some delicious Madhavi-made 'poha' and 'sabud dhana'.

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Guests At The Gada House - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Throwback
snippet.description:
Episode 1186: Guests At The Gada House 
---------------------------------------------------
Tusshar Kapoor and Vinay Pathak in Gada House - All the members of the Gada Family are surprised to see the star cast of Bajate Raho. Daya, Jethalal, and Bapuji are excited to meet Actors Tusshar Kapoor, Vinay Pathak, and Vishakha. Is there a surprise waiting for Gada Family?

Show Name- Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast -  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Shailesh Lodha
Full Episode - 1186
Produced By - Asit Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #à¤¤à¤¾à¤°à¤•à¤®à¥‡à¤¹à¤¤à¤¾à¤•à¤¾à¤‰à¤²à¥à¤Ÿà¤¾à¤šà¤¶à¥à¤®à¤¾ #SAB

Click here to Subscribe to SAB Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/sabtv?sub_confirmation=1

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

Click to watch all the episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7a6aWvIzLwbDe6FzzowRhMq
